Package com.promis.rtti.annotations

Annotation Types Summary
GenerateMethods Identifies class for which method information will be generated
GenerateRtti Identifies class for which RTTI will be generated Note that all public nested classes will also get RTTI info.
Index Use to specify RttiField index
NoAssign Identifies a class for which no assign code will be generated.
ReadOnly Use to specify read-only RttiField
RttiPackage Use to specify packages that hold RttiObjects Create package-info.java for required package like this:
@RttiPackage
package com.some.data.package;

import com.promis.rtti.annotations.RttiPackage;
 Subsequently all classes of this package will be probed and descendants of RttiObject or classes identified by GenerateRtti will get RTTI.
